text: Tsvyatko Pashkulev (4 February 1945 – 1 November 2019) was a Bulgarian wrestler.На 74-годишна възраст почина Цвятко Пашкулев He competed in the men's Greco-Roman bantamweight at the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1945 births Category:2019 deaths Category:Place of birth missing Category:Bulgarian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Bulgaria Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics
